    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>This video showcases a Drush plugin called <a href="http://drupal.org/project/dslm">DSLM</a> which stands for Drush Symbolic Link Manager.  It's an alternative to core multi-site which puts the developer first when managing lots of sites in the same area.  There are also a few patches I have in the queue that add additional functionality like sharing of large chunks of modules, themes, and libraries.</p></div></div></div>
